{
  "stem": "7592.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were about 15,000 people staying over there watching this.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this, at that time, there was no law-- the German later changed the law-- you cannot kill somebody in concentration until you get the upper approval from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You have to-- this was after, you know, outside, and the Red Cross start searching, asking questions.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they have to report over there the reason why.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was one scene over there when they killed this guy from-- who was chief of the police, who was Goeth's right hand.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they were liquidating.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He got an order, Goeth, to finish off this Chilowitch because he knew too much.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So Goeth says, no, I know him, and I trust him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He's never going to squeal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they said, we can prove it to you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Other-- other Germans in camp.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What they did, they set up one of the Ukrainian guards to sell him a gun so he can run away from the camp.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He went with this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, you know, he was with us-- came in and he ask us for money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We gave him money, we gave him material for Goeth, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He came one day, he says, listen, I need some money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I said, we haven't got because we didn't have contact with the outside because they closed the camp for a few days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So he went to his brother-in-law, which was our they called it-- policeman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "OD, he used to bring us to-- from barracks to the place where we worked, and brought us back.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, with the uniform there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He went to ask him, outside thing, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He gave him some money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he was observed already by the German.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
